# Compiled main-package binaries dropped at the repo root by
# `go build ./<main-pkg>/`. Each entry is a main package's leaf directory name
# (the binary it produces). When a name also matches a root-level source
# directory (akita, daisen2), the directory is re-included so its source stays
# tracked. Add new main packages here, or build with `-o`.
/akita
!/akita/
!/akita/**
/daisen2
